# Rust build output. The shipped artifact is swc-plugin/annotate.wasm (tracked).
target/
*/swc-plugin/target/
Cargo.lock
# ...but the swc-plugin lock IS tracked: it pins swc_core + its plugin host ABI so
# CI rebuilds the wasm reproducibly. An open caret range (swc_core = "68") let CI
# resolve a newer 68.x whose plugin ABI dropped host symbols → wasm link failure.
!annotate/swc-plugin/Cargo.lock
